spelling], good Middle Persian name,

00:14:45.070 --> 00:14:48.190
and his father was
from Bahl in Bactria.

00:14:48.190 --> 00:14:54.420
Another [inaudible] found
in China a little bit later,

00:14:54.420 --> 00:14:57.750
