A pillar that overlooks the
city you'll find [inaudible].

00:32:04.910 --> 00:32:10.250
You also find some very
famous old mosaics.

00:32:10.250 --> 00:32:12.350
So, for example, here,
you find Syriac,

00:32:12.350 --> 00:32:17.580
or a derivative upon this mosaic
