01:10:39.410 --> 01:10:41.220
to memory and what memory does.

01:10:41.220 --> 01:10:42.760
This is a huge discussion.

01:10:42.760 --> 01:10:48.460
There are many factors that
played in its development

01:10:48.460 --> 01:10:50.690
and in its changing over time.

01:10:50.690 --> 01:10:53.540
There were many cultures
that were mixing,

01:10:53.540 --> 01:10:57.170
as we heard, only on this panel.

01:10:57.170 --> 01:10:59.500
So musical influences
went in and out

01:10:59.500 --> 01:11:01.850
in various sorts of
ways and directions.

01:11:01.850 --> 01:11:06.210
