put their sacred texts to music,

01:11:13.900 --> 01:11:16.300
to musical sounds that they are --

01:11:16.300 --> 01:11:19.960
to ways of chanting that
they considered very valuable

01:11:19.960 --> 01:11:21.290
and very important.

01:11:21.290 --> 01:11:23.930
